org.hibernate.ogm.util.impl

Interface Log

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.jboss.logging.BasicLogger
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Log, Log, Log, Log, Log, Log, Log

    @MessageLogger(projectCode="OGM")
public interface Log
extends org.jboss.logging.BasicLogger
    Log messages and exceptions used by Hibernate OGM core. Dialects may provide extensions of this interface with their own specific log messages.

    The following intervals for the message ids are to be used:

    • 1-1000: core
    • 1101-1200: infinispan
    • 1201-1300: mongob
    • 1301-1400: couchdb
    • 1401-1500: neo4j
    • 1501-1600: ehcache
    • 1601-1700: redis
    Author:
    Sanne Grinovero <sanne@hibernate.org> (C) 2011 Red Hat Inc., Gunnar Morling
